25a StPO) and the first part of the procedures for conducting the main hearing (up to § 255a StPO). The 2017 “Act for a more effective and practical design of criminal procedure” modified §§ 213, 254, 244, 251, and 254; this is the first legal commentary to comprehensively explain these changes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aCriminal procedurezGermany. 4aHauptverhandlung. 4aStPO. 4aStrafprozessrecht. 4aStrafrecht. 4aStrafverfahren. 7aLAW / Criminal Procedure.2bisacsh  aMain hearing.1 aBecker, Jörg-Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCirener, Gabriele, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHerausgeber, Die, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJäger, Christian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMosbacher, Andreas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSander, Günther M., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2019z9783110606249oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831103811770 cprintz978311027477640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311027494340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110274943423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110274943.jpg  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019